data.description: *Job Relocation Prompts Motivated Sellers! *In the Sweet Spot of The River Club Gated Community *So Close To Charlotte Harbor! *Spacious-With a Total of 3459 sq ft, 3 Bdr, 5 Ba, Pool/Spa, 3 Car Garage, SMART Home~with a 240 Volt Electric car charger! *This Stately Abode Welcomes you with Open Space, Ample Natural Light and a Layout Design for Modern Living. *Offering-Impact Doors & Windows, 12 Ft Tray Ceilings, Tile Floors, Custom Window Treatments, Wood Cabinetry, Granite Counters, Walk-in Pantry Closet, Upgraded Lighting Fixtures, High Quality LG Black SS Appliances, Dual Vanities, H&H Walk-in Closets, Plenty of Storage Space, Spacious Lanai has Electric and Plumbing ready for your Outdoor Kitchen, Paver Driveway, Front Entry & Pool Lanai  *Ideal for Entertaining Friends and Family Inside and Out *Make it Your Private oasis, Where the Screened-in Pool & Spa awaits, *If you’re seeking a Home that Combines Luxury, Convenience and an Attractive Lifestyle Look No Further. 24040 Riverfront Drive Delivers all that and more making it Truly an Exceptional Find. *Live in a Community that Offers Resort Style Amenities such as refreshing Portfolio Equipped Gym all with the safety and privacy of the Gated Community Environment. If you Enjoy Relaxing by the Poolside, Staying Active in the Gym or Exploring nearby Beaches this Home Provides the Ideal base for your Preferred Lifestyle. *5 min. to Picturesque Waterfront of Charlotte Harbor, Downtown Historic Punta Gorda *Enjoy the Charm of a Harbor Walk *Fishing, Boating, Waterfront Dining, Shopping, Biking, Pickleball, Golfing and Plenty of Entertainment Options within 10 min. The convenience doesn’t stop there with easy access to I-75, you effortlessly explore nearby cities such as Fort Myers and Sarasota both just a short drive away. Punta Gorda airport is within  10 minutes ensuring direct flights to many U.S. destinations. Schedule a viewing today and Start Living the Florida Dream!
